com.github.systemdir.gml

Class YedGmlWriter<V,E,G>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.systemdir.gml.YedGmlWriter<V,E,G>

  • public class YedGmlWriter<V,E,G>
extends Object
    Exports a graph into a GML file (Graph Modelling Language) for yED.

    For a description of the format see http://www.infosun.fmi.uni-passau.de/Graphlet/GML/.

    Author:
    (GML writer) Dimitrios Michail, (yED extension) Hayato Hess
